  "title": "Marketing Campaign Ambassador (Entry-level)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚀 We Are Expanding! 🚀</strong><br>\nIf you’re self-driven, outgoing, and sharp... <strong>We want YOU!</strong> 🌟</p>\n<p>Our organization aims to be the <strong>top sales and marketing firm</strong> in Singapore, representing a range of professional and high-profile clients to boost their sales revenue. 📈</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>🧐 Qualify consumers based on set criteria and manage the communication throughout the entire sales cycle—from introduction of products to onboarding.</li>\n  <li>💬 Drive customer acquisition through face-to-face interaction.</li>\n  <li>📝 Develop content for engaging sales presentations.</li>\n  <li>🎉 Run and oversee campaigns and events to elevate our brand presence.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Perks:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>🌍 Overseas opportunities – Regional and International!</li>\n  <li>🌟 Gain first-hand experience from top-performing individuals.</li>\n  <li>🤝 Mentorship to ensure you thrive in a fully performance-based industry.</li>\n  <li>🎉 Vibrant team culture where you’ll feel at home.</li>\n  <li>🏆 Rewards for your achievements and dedication.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Good to Have:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>✨ Positive learning attitude</li>\n  <li>💪 Self-driven and motivated</li>\n  <li>🤝 Team player</li>\n  <li>💬 Strong interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>👩‍💼 Leadership skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have what it takes, we would LOVE to speak with you! 💥</p>",
